          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“头一名祥梅寺变律。”"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二鬼夺册同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊吓吓！唬杀我也！我说昨夜做的梦不好，梦见空中一条黄龙飞到寺中，伸出"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "二鬼→鬼甲",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "鬼甲→变律",
