    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "变律",
        "黄巢"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄巢上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，黄巢。上京应试，圣上见我人物丑陋，将俺剥去衣冠，逐出朝门。我想大"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（锁南枝） 吾生身三十秋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜上上之兆。弥陀菩萨，大事若成，重修庙宇，再整金身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（变律上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃布衣闲士，和尚为何口称“万岁”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁乃真命之主，请到禅房。和尚有话，奏上万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "引道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和尚甚么话说来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（锁南枝） 琉璃内点尽油，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那鬼使偷油何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真主是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和尚有所不知。俺上京科举，圣上道我人物丑陋，将俺逐出朝门，永不赴考。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下皆是皇爷疆土，何言借乎？贫僧有羊羔鹿脯，不敢进献。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有美馔取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和尚不必悲啼，有甚么事说上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大殿有盏琉璃。每次添油十斤，也点三五昼夜。今来添上油就没有了。我只说"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那鬼偷油何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和尚也曾问他，他说黄天子出世，阴司造册，缺少灯油，故此来取。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你问他黄天子何等人物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说黄天子横眉一字，面带金钱，鼻生三孔，牙排二齿。杀人八百万，血流三"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀的都是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说记不得许多，有底册拿去看。头一名……"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁赦过贫僧好奏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说俺饶过他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头一名祥梅寺住持变律。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿去开刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是贫僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪道和尚这般殷勤。今日已见，他日相逢，乃是故人，怎忍杀之？只是俺明日"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邂逅遇殷勤，从今是故人。感恩并积恨，万岁不生尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和尚送万岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不消。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄巢、变律同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "变律→黄巢",
          "turns": 13
        },
        {
          "edge": "黄巢→变律",
          "turns": 12
