    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "军士",
        "变律",
        "黄巢"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄巢起兵，过场，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（变律上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟鸣钟擂鼓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（挂葫芦） 如来望正盟，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慈悲救小僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搭救弟子免灾星。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人内同喊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "变律 （挂葫芦） 心急急，步慌忙，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀声闻四野似豺狼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看看将傍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此钟楼，躲在上面，黄天子人马过去，下来未迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（挂葫芦） 钟楼藏隐好商量，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "其实真停当，真停当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "躲得妙，躲得妙！不好！黄天子人马从此处经过，楼上有个和尚，拿下来开刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（挂葫芦） 虎啖羊，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "其实不停当，不停当。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（挂葫芦） 千思想，万忖量，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "处处兴兵将。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看看将傍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是山门，不免上去躲在上面，黄天子人马过去，我下来未迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（挂葫芦） 山门藏隐有商量，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "其实真停当，真停当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "躲得妙，躲得妙！不好！黄天子人马从此处经过，山门上有个和尚，拿去开刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（挂葫芦） 被他拿住。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "镇军民拥贯京都。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急忙移步奔前途。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "菩萨料应相拥护，相拥护。"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此一棵枯树，待我躲在里面，黄天子人马过去，出来未迟。欲赴旷山径，躲"
        },
        {
          "character": "变律",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在深山枯树中。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄巢率众将同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀气满乾坤，要整山河一统。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大小三军，前面不拘鸡犬牛羊，拿去开刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "军士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王，无鸡犬牛羊，只有枯树阻路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就拿枯树开刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "军士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王：有一个和尚头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿来我看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！原来是变律的首级。未曾起兵，先杀故友，好不败孤之兴也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "军士",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "定业难逃，何足虑哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄巢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就此杀上前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（水底鱼） 擂鼓摇旗，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三军号令齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇家一统归。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
